




{"id":5025,"date":"2021-07-19T10:06:26","date_gmt":"2021-07-19T03:06:26","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/?p=5025"},"modified":"2022-05-19T17:02:19","modified_gmt":"2022-05-19T10:02:19","slug":"lua-chon-man-hinh-tuong-tac-cho-trung-tam-ngoai-ngu","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/lua-chon-man-hinh-tuong-tac-cho-trung-tam-ngoai-ngu\/","title":{"rendered":"L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cho trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_78 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\" style=\"cursor:inherit\">N\u1ed9i dung ch\u00ednh<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/lua-chon-man-hinh-tuong-tac-cho-trung-tam-ngoai-ngu\/#tong_quan_ve_man_hinh_tuong_tac_cho_trung_tam_ngoai_ngu\" >T\u1ed5ng quan v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cho trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/lua-chon-man-hinh-tuong-tac-cho-trung-tam-ngoai-ngu\/#kinh_nghiem_lua_chon_man_hinh_tuong_tac_cho_trung_tam_ngoai_ngu\" >Kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cho trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cho trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu trong vi\u1ec7c truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c cho h\u1ecdc sinh. Nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c, vi\u1ec7c d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c trung t\u00e2m tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n. C\u00e1c em gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp thu t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u1edbi m\u1ed7i b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc, ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n c\u00e1c gi\u00e1c quan c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng th\u00f4ng qua vi\u1ec7c t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi \u00e2m thanh, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc v\u00e0 ch\u1ea1m t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c.<\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch tr\u00ean, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng, l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y thay v\u00ec nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c c\u1ed5 truy\u1ec1n nh\u01b0 \u201cc\u1ee5c ph\u1ea5n + c\u00e1i b\u1ea3ng, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 b\u1ea3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c (c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 l\u1ed7i th\u1eddi)\u201d. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c lo\u1ea1i m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cho trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y, Sao Mai s\u1ebd t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p nh\u1eefng\u00a0<b>kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft khi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cho trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef.\u00a0<\/b><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-5742 size-full aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/M%C3%A0n-h%C3%ACnh-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%C3%A1c-cho-trung-t%C3%A2m-ngo%E1%BA%A1i-ng%E1%BB%AF-3.jpg\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/M\u00e0n-h\u00ecnh-t\u01b0\u01a1ng-t\u00e1c-cho-trung-t\u00e2m-ngo\u1ea1i-ng\u1eef-3.jpg 800w, https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/M\u00e0n-h\u00ecnh-t\u01b0\u01a1ng-t\u00e1c-cho-trung-t\u00e2m-ngo\u1ea1i-ng\u1eef-3-796x400.jpg 796w, https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/M\u00e0n-h\u00ecnh-t\u01b0\u01a1ng-t\u00e1c-cho-trung-t\u00e2m-ngo\u1ea1i-ng\u1eef-3-768x386.jpg 768w, https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/M\u00e0n-h\u00ecnh-t\u01b0\u01a1ng-t\u00e1c-cho-trung-t\u00e2m-ngo\u1ea1i-ng\u1eef-3-24x12.jpg 24w, https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/M\u00e0n-h\u00ecnh-t\u01b0\u01a1ng-t\u00e1c-cho-trung-t\u00e2m-ngo\u1ea1i-ng\u1eef-3-36x18.jpg 36w, https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/M\u00e0n-h\u00ecnh-t\u01b0\u01a1ng-t\u00e1c-cho-trung-t\u00e2m-ngo\u1ea1i-ng\u1eef-3-48x24.jpg 48w, https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/M\u00e0n-h\u00ecnh-t\u01b0\u01a1ng-t\u00e1c-cho-trung-t\u00e2m-ngo\u1ea1i-ng\u1eef-3-600x302.jpg 600w\" alt=\"M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cho trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef\" width=\"800\" height=\"402\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tong_quan_ve_man_hinh_tuong_tac_cho_trung_tam_ngoai_ngu\"><\/span><b>T\u1ed5ng quan v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cho trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1eafc l\u1ef1c cho gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i 4.0 gi\u00fap mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1n h\u00fat h\u1ecdc sinh t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c trung t\u00e2m Anh Ng\u1eef v\u00e0 Ngo\u1ea1i Ng\u1eef. V\u1ec1 t\u1ed5ng quan,\u00a0<strong>m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cho trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef<\/strong>\u00a0gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc tivi kh\u1ed5 l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng b\u1eb1ng b\u00fat ho\u1eb7c b\u1eb1ng tay tr\u00ean \u0111\u00f3. V\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng n\u00e0y, c\u1ea3 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc sinh \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 linh ho\u1ea1t trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi nhau ngay tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<p><strong>M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c<\/strong>\u00a0c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c c\u00f9ng l\u00fac t\u1eeb 10 \u0111\u1ebfn 20 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh thay v\u00ec th\u00f4ng qua m\u00e1y chi\u1ebfu. M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 cao c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u00e0 video ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 4K kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i cho m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh khi nh\u00ecn nhi\u1ec1u. V\u00ec v\u1eady ch\u00fang h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 th\u00f4ng tin nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 tr\u1ef1c quan \u0111\u1ebfn cho h\u1ecdc sinh. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh LED c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n m\u00e1y t\u00ednh hay b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5734 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/M%C3%A0n-h%C3%ACnh-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%C3%A1c-cho-trung-t%C3%A2m-ngo%E1%BA%A1i-ng%E1%BB%AF-2.jpg\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/M\u00e0n-h\u00ecnh-t\u01b0\u01a1ng-t\u00e1c-cho-trung-t\u00e2m-ngo\u1ea1i-ng\u1eef-2.jpg 800w, https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/M\u00e0n-h\u00ecnh-t\u01b0\u01a1ng-t\u00e1c-cho-trung-t\u00e2m-ngo\u1ea1i-ng\u1eef-2-534x400.jpg 534w, https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/M\u00e0n-h\u00ecnh-t\u01b0\u01a1ng-t\u00e1c-cho-trung-t\u00e2m-ngo\u1ea1i-ng\u1eef-2-768x575.jpg 768w, https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/M\u00e0n-h\u00ecnh-t\u01b0\u01a1ng-t\u00e1c-cho-trung-t\u00e2m-ngo\u1ea1i-ng\u1eef-2-24x18.jpg 24w, https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/M\u00e0n-h\u00ecnh-t\u01b0\u01a1ng-t\u00e1c-cho-trung-t\u00e2m-ngo\u1ea1i-ng\u1eef-2-36x27.jpg 36w, https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/M\u00e0n-h\u00ecnh-t\u01b0\u01a1ng-t\u00e1c-cho-trung-t\u00e2m-ngo\u1ea1i-ng\u1eef-2-48x36.jpg 48w, https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/M\u00e0n-h\u00ecnh-t\u01b0\u01a1ng-t\u00e1c-cho-trung-t\u00e2m-ngo\u1ea1i-ng\u1eef-2-600x449.jpg 600w\" alt=\"Ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cho trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef\" width=\"800\" height=\"599\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi c\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng \u01b0u vi\u1ec7t,\u00a0<strong>m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cho trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef<\/strong>\u00a0\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cung c\u1ea5p b\u1edfi\u00a0<b>Inno Vi\u1ec7t Nam<\/b> cam k\u1ebft ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t trong c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y, l\u01b0u tr\u1eef v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd b\u00e0i gi\u1ea3ng, n\u1ed9i dung b\u1ed5 tr\u1ee3.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"kinh_nghiem_lua_chon_man_hinh_tuong_tac_cho_trung_tam_ngoai_ngu\"><\/span><b>Kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cho trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><b>Th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cho trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef<\/b><\/h3>\n<p><b><\/b>T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed hay c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, v\u00e0\u00a0<strong>m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c<\/strong>\u00a0c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3. Tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u kh\u00e1c nhau t\u1eeb cao c\u1ea5p, trung c\u1ea5p cho t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m gi\u00e1 b\u00ecnh d\u00e2n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00e2u d\u00e0i th\u00ec n\u00ean c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u uy t\u00edn tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 gi\u00e1 th\u00e0nh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng \u0111i k\u00e8m theo \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5733 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/M%C3%A0n-h%C3%ACnh-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%C3%A1c-cho-trung-t%C3%A2m-ngo%E1%BA%A1i-ng%E1%BB%AF-1.jpg\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/M\u00e0n-h\u00ecnh-t\u01b0\u01a1ng-t\u00e1c-cho-trung-t\u00e2m-ngo\u1ea1i-ng\u1eef-1.jpg 800w, https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/M\u00e0n-h\u00ecnh-t\u01b0\u01a1ng-t\u00e1c-cho-trung-t\u00e2m-ngo\u1ea1i-ng\u1eef-1-711x400.jpg 711w, https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/M\u00e0n-h\u00ecnh-t\u01b0\u01a1ng-t\u00e1c-cho-trung-t\u00e2m-ngo\u1ea1i-ng\u1eef-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/M\u00e0n-h\u00ecnh-t\u01b0\u01a1ng-t\u00e1c-cho-trung-t\u00e2m-ngo\u1ea1i-ng\u1eef-1-24x14.jpg 24w, https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/M\u00e0n-h\u00ecnh-t\u01b0\u01a1ng-t\u00e1c-cho-trung-t\u00e2m-ngo\u1ea1i-ng\u1eef-1-36x20.jpg 36w, https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/M\u00e0n-h\u00ecnh-t\u01b0\u01a1ng-t\u00e1c-cho-trung-t\u00e2m-ngo\u1ea1i-ng\u1eef-1-48x27.jpg 48w, https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/M\u00e0n-h\u00ecnh-t\u01b0\u01a1ng-t\u00e1c-cho-trung-t\u00e2m-ngo\u1ea1i-ng\u1eef-1-600x338.jpg 600w\" alt=\"C\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cho trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3><b>Ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cho trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef<\/b><\/h3>\n<p>N\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/man-hinh-led-tuong-tac\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c<\/strong><\/a>\u00a0th\u00ec nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e1ng quan t\u00e2m sau:<br \/>\n<b><\/b><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh s\u1eafc n\u00e9t, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb9p<\/li>\n<li>C\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng nh\u1ea1y, m\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u00e0 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng cao<\/li>\n<li>\u0110\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh: Ngay t\u1eeb khung, vi\u1ec1n m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, c\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c n\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 l\u1edbp k\u00ednh c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ch\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea7y x\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 va \u0111\u1eadp.<\/li>\n<li>Th\u1eddi gian b\u1ea3o h\u00e0nh: L\u00e0 thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed th\u00ec th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch b\u1ea3o h\u00e0nh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u00eau ch\u00ed r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. N\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Sao Mai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o h\u00e0nh 2 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng tin v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 an t\u00e2m cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><b>K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cho trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef<\/b><\/h3>\n<p>M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cho trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u k\u00edch th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1c nhau nh\u01b0ng theo th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec c\u00e1c trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc 55 inch-86 inch. V\u1edbi k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y th\u00ec h\u1ecdc sinh s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng thao t\u00e1c v\u00e0 quan s\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ean to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5731 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/K%C3%ADch-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bc-m%C3%A0n-h%C3%ACnh-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%C3%A1c.jpg\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/K\u00edch-th\u01b0\u1edbc-m\u00e0n-h\u00ecnh-t\u01b0\u01a1ng-t\u00e1c.jpg 800w, https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/K\u00edch-th\u01b0\u1edbc-m\u00e0n-h\u00ecnh-t\u01b0\u01a1ng-t\u00e1c-768x348.jpg 768w, https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/K\u00edch-th\u01b0\u1edbc-m\u00e0n-h\u00ecnh-t\u01b0\u01a1ng-t\u00e1c-24x11.jpg 24w, https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/K\u00edch-th\u01b0\u1edbc-m\u00e0n-h\u00ecnh-t\u01b0\u01a1ng-t\u00e1c-36x16.jpg 36w, https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/K\u00edch-th\u01b0\u1edbc-m\u00e0n-h\u00ecnh-t\u01b0\u01a1ng-t\u00e1c-48x22.jpg 48w, https:\/\/saomaiedu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/K\u00edch-th\u01b0\u1edbc-m\u00e0n-h\u00ecnh-t\u01b0\u01a1ng-t\u00e1c-600x272.jpg 600w\" alt=\"K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cho trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef\" width=\"800\" height=\"363\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3><b>M\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cho trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef<\/b><\/h3>\n<p>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 m\u1eaft l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u00eau ch\u00ed quan tr\u1ecdng khi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cho trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef. Nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 sau \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 l\u1ecdc \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng xanh: gi\u00fap gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc sinh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh l\u00e2u h\u01a1n m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1edfi \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng xanh<\/li>\n<li>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ch\u1ed1ng nh\u00e1y: gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf nh\u00e1y m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 \u00edt \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t<\/li>\n<li>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ch\u1ed1ng ch\u00f3i: Gi\u00fap m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb r\u00f5 n\u00e9t, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb l\u00f3a ngay c\u1ea3 trong ph\u00f2ng nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u01b0u \u00fd v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft khi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn\u00a0<strong>m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cho trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef<\/strong>. N\u1ebfu qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 th\u1eafc m\u1eafc g\u00ec th\u00ec h\u00e3y li\u00ean l\u1ea1c ngay cho Inno Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 Inno c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch. V\u00e0 r\u1ea5t mong nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1ed9i dung m\u00e0 Inno cung c\u1ea5p cho qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cho trung t\u00e2m ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu trong vi\u1ec7c truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c cho h\u1ecdc sinh. Nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c, vi\u1ec7c d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c trung t\u00e2m tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n&#8230;.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":9117,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[66],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-5025","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tin-tuc"],"acf":